name: BOOBS BATTLEGROUND
description:
War has been waged across the island of Lesbia. Nazi-feminists hordes invaded territory.
And you have to play a key role in this battle.

Fight against many enemies. Travel freely around the island.
Find a way to open the gates of the enemy castle and defeat the main enemy.

Stop the feminists.

Features:
  • Open world
  • Different weapons and enemies
  • Exciting combat system
  • 5000 achievements
